@startuml
title E6-01 — Propose and Approve Debt Transaction\nActor and Decision View

left to right direction

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

skinparam nodesep 110
skinparam ranksep 130
skinparam padding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 25

skinparam rectangle {
  FontSize 15
  MinimumWidth 190
}

actor "Issuance\nOfficer" as Officer

rectangle "Debt Issuance Platform" as Platform {

  rectangle "Create Proposal\n\nValidate Terms" as Create

  rectangle "Control Approval\n\nWorkflow" as Control

  rectangle "Record Decision\n\nUpdate Status" as Record
}

actor "Treasury\nApprover" as Approver

' Layout guidance
Officer -[hidden]-> Create
Create -[hidden]-> Control
Control -[hidden]-> Record
Record -[hidden]-> Approver

Officer --> Create : Propose
Create --> Officer : Validation

Officer --> Control : Submit
Control --> Approver : Review request

Approver --> Control : Approve\nor return

Control --> Record : Decision
Record --> Officer : Final status

legend bottom
|= Actor |= Main responsibility |
| Issuance Officer | Propose and submit the debt transaction |
| Platform | Validate, control workflow and record decisions |
| Treasury Approver | Independently approve or return the proposal |

Main flow:

Propose → Validate → Submit → Review → Decide → Record
endlegend

@enduml